issue.body:
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Logging in with Tellmewhen enabled
2. Still buggs with no profile loaded
3. Not fixed when reinstalled + deleted tellmewhen.lua files in wtf.

What do you expect to happen? What happens instead?
Just a bugreport. When logging in the wow-client warns me: "There are too many errors in your UI. As a results, your game experience may be degraded. disable or update the failing addons if you dont want to see this message again."

What version of TellMeWhen are you using? ("The latest" is not a version)
v6.2.6

Do you have an error log of what happened?

comments.body:
These are non-breaking errors, so they are not going to cause any sort of performance degradation. To fix it, install the latest alpha version of TellMeWhen from the files tab at the top of this page.


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
